OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIsraeli curbs on Orthodox  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FEaster event criticised    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Church leaders in Jerusalem say Israeli
OL,6, police are imposing "heavy-handed and  
OL,7, unnecessary restrictions" on access to 
OL,8, an important Orthodox Easter ritual.   
OL,10,FThey say numbers who can attend        
OL,11,FSaturday's Holy Fire ceremony at the   
OL,12,FHoly Sepulchre Church are being limited
OL,13,Fto 1,800, down from 10,000 last year.  
OL,15,FThe police, who control security in    
OL,16,Foccupied East Jerusalem, say they are  
OL,17,Fensuring safety and freedom of worship.
OL,19,FChurch officials are now urging        
OL,20,FChristians to ignore the restrictions. 
